Package br.usp.poli.takiyama.prv

Interface Summary
LogicalVariable A logical variable is a word starting with an upper-case letter or the underscore.
Operator<E extends RangeElement> A commutative and associative binary operator, such as AND and OR.
Prv PRV stands for Parameterized Random Variable, a structure that represents sets of random variables.
RangeElement This class represents elements from parameterized random variable ranges.
Replaceable<T> Class that represents objects over which Substitution is applicable.
Term A term is either a variable or a constant.
